### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### Login and capture access token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Get profile
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Start a 25 minute pomodoro
POST http://localhost:8000/api/timers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Deep Work",
  "duration_seconds": 1500
}

@timerId = {{last.response.body.id}}

### Fetch live tick (long poll with wait=false)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/timers/{{timerId}}/tick?wait=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel the active timer
POST http://localhost:8000/api/timers/{{timerId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
